e did not show any significant findings.\nBEAUTY ONLY and FLAME HERO were sent for sampling.", "Dayofweek": "Sunday", "Place3Div": "68.00", "Sec4time": "00:00:24", "Raceclass": "Class 2", "RunningPosition": "9 8 7 12", "ThisDouble12Div": "58.50", "Surface": "TURF", "RacecourseCode": "ST", "Trainer": "J Size", "Treble111Div": "361.00", "RaceNumber": 10, "DeclarHorseWt": 1138, "Sec4DBL": 11.75}
